original_title: Неизбежность или как Дима влюбился в Инну
overview: Student Inna rents a room from her grandmother and dives headlong into her studies without wasting any more time. But, at the same time, she does not know that a noisy neighbor lives above her, who disrupts her plans for study, and possibly her personal life.
title: Inevitability or How Dima Fell In Love With Inna
